c: 34
v: 31
t: "Those who disbelieve say: \"We will not believe in this Qur’an, nor in any (Message) that came before it.\" If you could but see when such wrongdoers are made to stand before their Lord, throwing back blame at one another! Those who (in the world) were oppressed (and did not oppose being oppressed, humiliated, and misled) say to those who acted in arrogance and oppressed others: \"Had it not been for you, we would have been true believers"